org.apache.juneau.http.response

Class AlreadyReported

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.http.response.BasicHttpResponse
      • org.apache.juneau.http.response.AlreadyReported
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.http.HttpMessage, org.apache.http.HttpResponse

    @Response
 @StatusCode(value=208)
 @Schema(description="Already Reported")
public class AlreadyReported
extends BasicHttpResponse
    Represents an HTTP 208 Already Reported response.

    The members of a DAV binding have already been enumerated in a preceding part of the (multistatus) response, and are not being included again.
